text: Disney Princess is a media franchise and toy line by Disney. It features female characters of Disney productions like Snow White, Cinderella, Ariel and other princesses. ==Characters== * Snow White * Cinderella * Aurora * Ariel * Belle * Jasmine * Pocahontas * Mulan * Tiana * Rapunzel * Merida * Moana * Raya ==Other websites== *Official Disney Princess website Category:Disney characters Category:Lists of fictional characters Category:Media franchises Category:Movie characters Category:Television characters
